```plantuml
@startuml ruoccofabrizio_azure-open-ai-embeddings-qna

actor User
participant "Streamlit Web App" as WebApp
participant "Azure OpenAI Service" as OpenAI
participant "Vector Store (Azure/Redis/PGVector)" as VectorStore
participant "Azure Function: BatchStartProcessing" as BatchStart
participant "Azure Function: BatchPushResults" as BatchPush
participant "Azure Queue" as AzureQueue
participant "Azure Blob Storage" as BlobStorage

User -> WebApp: Enter question
WebApp -> OpenAI: Create embeddings from question
OpenAI -> WebApp: Return question embeddings
WebApp -> VectorStore: Retrieve similar documents using embeddings
VectorStore -> WebApp: Return document chunks
WebApp -> OpenAI: Send chunks + question for answer generation
OpenAI -> WebApp: Return generated answer
WebApp -> User: Display answer

note over WebApp: Asynchronous Batch Processing

User -> BatchStart: HTTP request to start batch processing
BatchStart -> AzureQueue: Add message to queue
AzureQueue -> BatchPush: Trigger function with queue message
BatchPush -> BlobStorage: Read documents from storage
BatchPush -> OpenAI: Extract text and create embeddings
OpenAI -> VectorStore: Add embeddings to vector store

@enduml
```